  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.discovery.AbstractBluetoothDeviceDiscoverer<Space,Device>
  • Type Parameters:
    Space - Space type parameter which the discovered devices belong to

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    BluetoothDeviceDiscoverer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EddystoneDiscoverer, IBeaconDiscoverer

    public abstract class AbstractBluetoothDeviceDiscoverer<Space,Device extends RemoteBluetoothDevice>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BluetoothDeviceDiscoverer
    Abstraction for Bluetooth device discoverers in the SDK. The abstraction provides convenient interface whenever you need to implement your own Bluetooth device discoverer.
